Commands	Type ship	Operation		Range
-------------------------------------------------------------

A<AZIMUTH>		ALL	Set azimuth		(0-359)
B<BALLAST>		S	Set ballast %		(0-100)
				0 Sets buoyancy for depth 0
				100 Sets buoyancy for depth 17
B			S	Set buoyancy for present level
C<ARGUMENT>		B	Computer function
DB<DEPTH>		B,D	Drop bow charge		(1-16)
DS<DEPTH>		B,D	Drop stern chargE	(1-16)
EX			ALL	Exit
F<AZIMUTH>		B,D,P,H	Fire surface gun	(0-359)
G			ALL	Set monitor gag
K<KIND>			B,S,D,P	Set type at docking	(1-4)
L			D	Lay mine on surface
M<AZIMUTH><PITCH>	B,S,D,H	Fire missile		(0-359),(1-89)
N			ALL	New screen
N<SHIP NAME>		ALL	Set new ship name
P<PITCH>		S	Set submarine pitch	(-45-45)
P<PITCH>		H	Set helicopter pitch	(-90-90)
R<CHARACTER>		ALL	Radio messages to ally
S<SPEED>		ALL	Set speed		(-12-30)
SC<AZIMUTH>		ALL	Set sonar azimuth	(0-359)
SW<AZIMUTH><INC>	ALL	Sweep to azimuth by inc	(0-359,1-359)
SWC<INC>		ALL	Sweep forever by inc	(0-359)
SC			ALL	Lock sonar azimuth on ship's azimuth
T			S,P	Fire trpedo
W<CHARACTER>		ALL	Find out who character is
W			ALL	Find out positions of allies

(B=BATTLESHIP, S=SUBMARINE, D=DESTROYER, P=P.T. BOAT, H=HELICOPTER)


Computer function arguments:

<X,Y,ALTITUDE>	Find azimuth & elevation to fire missile at coordinate
G		If auto fire is off, turn it on, else, turn it off

